  "uuid": "0fc70e7e8be8222d66cfc25d6d11ef3b",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Brand Strategist",
  "description": "<p>Big Fred Pte. Ltd. is growing, and we’re looking for a <strong>Senior Brand Strategist</strong> to join us in shaping bold, meaningful brands at the intersection of <strong>strategy, design and business</strong>.</p><p>We partner with founders and organisations who want clarity, direction and brands that shape tomorrow. </p><h3>✨ What you’ll do</h3><p>As a Senior Brand Strategist, you’ll play a key role across projects, from discovery to delivery:</p><ul><li><p>Lead brand strategy projects end-to-end (research, synthesis, positioning, frameworks)</p></li><li><p>Plan and facilitate brand workshops with clients and internal teams</p></li><li><p>Turn insights into clear strategic narratives and actionable recommendations</p></li><li><p>Collaborate closely with designers, founders and other partners</p></li><li><p>Present confidently to senior stakeholders and guide decision-making</p></li><li><p>Support business development with strategic thinking and proposals</p></li></ul><h3>🎯 What we’re looking for</h3><ul><li><p>7+ years of experience in brand strategy (agency and/or consultancy side)</p></li><li><p>Strong experience with brand foundations: positioning, purpose, architecture, messaging</p></li><li><p>Comfortable leading workshops and client conversations</p></li><li><p>Strategic thinker who can also be hands-on with decks and frameworks</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication and storytelling skills</p></li><li><p>Calm, collaborative, and proactive - you take ownership and move things forward</p></li><li><p>Experience across different markets or cultures is a big plus<br /><strong></strong></p></li></ul>",
